e":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T04:26:58.000Z","msg":"聽完周殷廷嘅逃兵就喊左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係唔想淡到無左 <br />\n每次諗起你我都好心痛<br />\n分手真係唯一嘅解決方法咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d97e80a59fbe95579fed267c4e222eedb70e34","tid":216123,"uid":60937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T04:27:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實一切都係分手藉口,根本係對方想走</blockquote><br />\n淡左真係一個好on9既藉口<br />\n寧願你一五一十講清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98cd9ff238aa5624ca85de02168ca43ac9a587ca","tid":216123,"uid":60934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T04:33:59.000Z","msg":"我真係好掛住好掛住佢<br />\n差唔多每晚發夢都夢到佢<br />\n同佢好番哂 佢嘅感覺返哂黎<br />\n好可惜呢個只係一個夢<br />\n只要一醒番我就發現自己返番去現實<br />\n之後個心就會好痛 真係好痛<br />\n點解要咁樣 係咪我唔識拍拖<br />\n到底係咪我唔識得去維持一段感情 一段關係<br />\n點解我可以咁垃圾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd1813f1dc5846a1bfcafa35bf7113b3bf63ca7","tid":216123,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T04:34:53.000Z","msg":"肯坦白同你講再分手算係咁<br />\n好撚多帽你之後之分"},{"pid":"0b4ee84dce650e47a241d06eb5e7eb9c5c405020","tid":216123,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T04:35:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肯坦白同你講再分手算係咁<br />\n好撚多帽你之後<span style=\"color: red;\">先</span>分</blockquote>"},{"pid":"d5436b0366741bebe16e5c9a5a3be99ad5159e8e","tid":216123,"uid":9924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T04:36:33.000Z","msg":"變淡分手唔係基本野咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f61a32674abb0b7333efa4f3347ec14a9213d384","tid":216123